{"title":"中国人民心连心——为急赈治淮而作","authors":["吴岩"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民心连心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为急赈治淮而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民肉贴肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们患难相共，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们感情相通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派，留下灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决黄河，黄水夺淮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四千万亩良田受了灾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受灾的人民一千三百万！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民肉贴肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们患难相共，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们感情相通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河人民千千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参军送粮运子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命鲜血火样红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭转历史立大功！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河人民千千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万亩庄稼付东流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无家、无衣、食不周，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪滔天北风吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民肉贴肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们患难相共，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们感情相通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急赈，急赈！治淮，治淮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的政府医治历史的灾害；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四万六千二百万，支援一千三百万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破难关，来年大生产！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民肉贴肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们患难相共，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们感情相通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五○年十月十八日。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}